    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Surfaces BIC's open regulatory registry (licensees, registrants, wholesale-market businesses, fleet vehicles, violations, complaints) and adds apply_for_license \u2014 the net-new write workflow locked today inside the Salesforce Experience Cloud portal.",
